{
  "stem": "19982.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the funny thing is, when they told me that this-- that those two girls took out, I knew exactly the place where it was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because I remember before the war, we used to have such a tile-- big tiles ovens, such high-tile ovens.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I remember they-- my father was doing something near the oven in the wall with somebody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I asked him what he's doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he says, in case if it's a war, the, the-- they would throw gas, the gas shouldn't come in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when, listen, this was already six years later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when they told me that somebody took out something, I says, I'm going to tell you exactly which place this will be.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this time, I realized that this wasn't for gas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was they-- where they put away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, I never got anything from them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that's a different thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and we were traveling till we came to the town Wroclaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Came the time Wroclaw, I went way out and went to the shul to find out something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were some people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they told us, if you want, there is apartment-- a German apartment here you could go in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went, and I said to the wagon, we have an apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all the people which were on the wagon-- there were maybe a hundred, for sure-- we all went to this apartment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, one slept on top of the other, but didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We all went to this apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was already Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then It was Wroclaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was Breslau originally, but that was Wroclaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And slowly people started to take-- they got themselves different places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And everybody-- and we remained in this apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
